## 🚀 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Risfian111/Telemetry_Urban.git
cd Telemetry_Urban

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate        # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
```

`requirements.txt`

```
numpy>=1.24
pandas>=2.0
matplotlib>=3.7
scipy>=1.10
```

