## 💻 Usage

```bash
# 1. EDA
python modules/eda/telemetry_eda.py \
    --input data/raw/2026-02-22_01-25-41.csv

# 2. Transfer function identification
python modules/sysid/transfer_function.py \
    --input data/raw/351_GBT_MC75.csv

# 3. GA optimization
python modules/optimizer/genetic_algorithm.py \
    --tf-params data/processed/tf_results.json \
    --v-min 10 --v-max 45 \
    --generations 100 --pop 60

# 4. Path planning
python modules/pathplanner/dijkstra_astar.py \
    --input data/raw/2026-02-22_01-25-41.csv \
    --node-spacing 10 --algorithm astar
```

All dashboards are **standalone HTML files** — open directly in any browser, no server needed:

| File | Contents |
|---|---|
| `dashboards/telemetry_eda.html` | Time-series, energy, driving modes, KPI cards |
| `dashboards/transfer_function.html` | Bode plot, step response fit, PID table, closed-loop sim |
| `dashboards/ga_optimizer.html` | Convergence, chromosome viewer, strategy comparison |
| `dashboards/track_pathfinder.html` | GPS canvas map (zoom/pan/hover), speed & elevation profile |

