## 🗺 Roadmap

- [x] VESC telemetry parser & EDA dashboard
- [x] Transfer function identification (FOPDT, two-point method)
- [x] PID tuning — IMC, Ziegler-Nichols
- [x] GA throttle optimizer with TF-based vehicle simulator
- [x] GPS track extraction & lap detection
- [x] Graph construction — Haversine + elevation + curvature
- [x] Dijkstra & A\* pathfinding (minimum energy)
- [x] Interactive HTML dashboards (no external CDN dependencies)
- [ ] Integrate A\* per-segment speed limits into GA constraints
- [ ] NSGA-II multi-objective (Wh/km + thermal + battery SoH)
- [ ] IMU integration (roll/pitch/yaw) for cornering dynamics
- [ ] Online replanning with live GPS feed
- [ ] VESC firmware integration — CAN bus duty lookup table
- [ ] Neural network surrogate for faster GA fitness evaluation

